Package Collecto

Class Colour

  • java.lang.Object
    • Collecto.Colour
  • public class Colour
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is made for text colouring and consists of string of colour codes and methods to set the colour of a string.

    This class uses ANSI escape codes to handle colouring of the strings.

    See Also:
    TUI, Ball
